snippet.description:
Shot 100% on the HD HERO3® camera from ‪http://GoPro.com.

To celebrate Hieroglyphics' influential force in underground music and art for over 20 years, Oakland, CA Mayor Jean Quan, proclaimed September 3rd as Hiero Day.

Music
Souls of Mischief "Cab Fare"
